樣不獲澳洲承認，並被澳洲悉尼晨鋒報稱為文憑工廠（Diploma Mill ）[12]，2002年該校關閉[13]。其校長Douglass Capogrossi同年在夏威夷州開設另一教育機構Akamai University，同樣未獲美國政府認可。[10]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d654a3c59d688310e29bdd696fe71a3629fcdc03","tid":1244322,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"又比鄺仔踢爆"},{"pid":"bff4dbdd3c41f53d882717ce0761fc84a13ce47d","tid":1244322,"uid":17718,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭苦主大聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aeab3d67651bd11e6a17673db688480fd737fe","tid":1244322,"uid":174295,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:50:58.000Z","msg":"唉 又up返嗰套已經無人信嘅初心論"},{"pid":"1b53efe3992d1f95875f87b0b1a1091247ddf4a7","tid":1244322,"uid":163433,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"咩誤導巿民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你宜家講個啲野就真係誤導自己喇臭雞"},{"pid":"99a1b1c885b08221f372b3ba0768d5f2a5290ddd","tid":1244322,"uid":94102,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"打上去屌爆佢啦"},{"pid":"3c4f92d695a4784ca7fa17dc8d636b906c22c799","tid":1244322,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d44fb7a59355dab2a66a33aa2dbd4dbbe30ccd77","tid":1244322,"uid":163433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"聽緊港台一台<br />\n個條臭雞猛咁講警察幾咁慘<br />\n仲不斷話鄺神煽動白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話將事件政治化 擺警員做磨心 屌你咩 <br />\n主持都叫你收嗲 講講講 用下個豬腦先啦<br />\n啊係喎唔記得你個學位係買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gi