該島不受制於澳洲教育條例，所以該校學歷同樣不獲澳洲承認，並被澳洲悉尼晨鋒報稱為文憑工廠（Diploma Mill ）[12]，2002年該校關閉[13]。其校長Douglass Capogrossi同年在夏威夷州開設另一教育機構Akamai University，同樣未獲美國政府認可。[10]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36d27d1250649b76d2e76d10e921555deca58ec","tid":1244322,"uid":93563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"愈聽愈燥,反屌返反對果d人"},{"pid":"ddedf092d79a5737ebad91b7b7b005c075bc7178","tid":1244322,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"角博士假學歷乜事都冇，又話傷得一個就一個，有人恐嚇佢，走返支那啦，都冇人理妳。"},{"pid":"8e6ef55113ac43d7400d6c244cf56683a224ae36","tid":1244322,"uid":132302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"條友真係好似鄺仔話齋<br />\n係上去放火唔係救火<br />\n真係無腦㗎條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ecc0ec7df3536eb1e1da0cdc470343719b07a3","tid":1244322,"uid":93202,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d66633c08a3bc781cbee9c1337a366322f0b561a","tid":1244322,"uid":163433,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nERTM4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnERTM4e.png&h=57729df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解學歷個欄咩既都冇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no